snippet.title: Best VGM 677 - Atelier Iris 2 : The Azoth of Destiny - To the Underground Tunnel
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 1359 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sHduBNdadTA

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Playstation 2
Atelier Iris 2 : The Azoth of Destiny (2005)
To the Underground Tunnel
Ken Nakagawa & Daisuke Achiwa
